== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《愛，上了癮》獲得了影評人和觀眾的正面好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據83篇專業影評，持有88%的新鮮度，平均得分7.4／10<ref name="RT">{{cite web|url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chasing_amy/|title= Chasing Amy (1997)|work= [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher= [[Flixster|Flixster]]|accessdate= 2012-03-29|archive-date= 2012-04-20|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120420171631/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/chasing_amy/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則獲得71分，正評居多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/chasing-amy|title=Chasing Amy|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=2012-03-29|archive-date=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331083346/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/chasing-amy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。多數影評稱讚電影中的角色性向與性愛是原始且敏感，加上編導凱文·史密斯的幽默安排使電影更有層次。

據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應在A+到F間落在「A」<ref>{{cite web |author=Published on Apr 11, 1997 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,287470,00.html |title=Critical Mass |publisher=EW.com |date=1997-04-11 |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202224406/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,287470,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影在僅以25萬美元的預算下，在戲院共獲得了超過1200萬美元的票房<ref name="productions1"/><ref name="BOM"/><ref>Sciretta, Peter (January 21, 2015). [http://www.slashfilm.com/best-movies-of-sundance-film-festival-history/3/ "The Best Movies of Sundance Film Festival History 1985-1999"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/best-movies-of-sundance-film-festival-history/3/ |date=20170121005058 }}. [[愛，上了癮/Film|愛，上了癮//Film]].</ref>。

《愛，上了癮》在美國首映週末獲得了5萬2446美元的票房，位居當週票房排名第三<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=1997&wknd=14&p=.htm|title=April 4-6, 1997 Weekend|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|accessdate=2012-03-29|archive-date=2012-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513072319/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=1997&wknd=14&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在接下來的一週，電影在二十二間戲院中獲得了30萬2406美元的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=1997&wknd=15&p=.htm|title=April 11-13, 1997 Weekend|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|accessdate=2012-03-29|archive-date=2012-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130182647/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=1997&wknd=15&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

